'''{{lang|en|Musopen}}'''是设在美国加州塔扎纳的[[501(c)(3)|501(c)(3)]]非盈利机构，由Aaron Dunn于2005年发起，目标是以无版权的形式向公众免费提供音乐。

== 目标和行动 ==
Musopen是一個以[[公有領域|公有領域]]提供音樂作品的網上資料庫。雖然多數古典音樂[[樂譜|樂譜]]的版權已失效並進入[[公有領域|公有領域]]，但演奏並錄製成音樂的版權依然存在，Musopen的使命就是請人演奏這些樂譜並進行錄製，讓任何人可以自由下載、聆聽、使用或[[二次創作|二次創作]]，而不需要支付版權費。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.techdirt.com/articles/20100826/00301310779.shtml |title=Raising Money To Put Famous Classical Music Recordings Into The Public Domain |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2019-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190824032911/https://www.techdirt.com/articles/20100826/00301310779.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2010-08/26/musopen-public-domain |title=Musopen raises cash to open-source classical recordings |accessdate=2010-09-14 |archive-date=2010-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100929062953/http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2010-08/26/musopen-public-domain |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2008年，Musopen重新錄製32首[[貝多芬|貝多芬]]的鋼琴奏鳴曲，並放到公有領域上。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://arstechnica.com/old/content/2008/05/musopen-puts-classical-recordings-scores-in-public-domain.ars |title=Musopen puts classical recordings, scores in public domain |publisher=Ars Technica |date=22 May 2008 |accessdate=2014-09-20 |archive-date=2012-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120428224137/http://arstechnica.com/old/content/2008/05/musopen-puts-classical-recordings-scores-in-public-domain.ars |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2010年，Musopen從[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]募集到68,360美元雇用一支管弦樂隊來演奏古典音樂，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/Musopen/record-and-release-free-music-without-copyrights |title=Musopen在Kickstarter募集的頁面 |accessdate=2012-08-17 |archive-date=2012-06-19 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68Xm988EO?url=http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/Musopen/record-and-release-free-music-without-copyrights |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://internet.solidot.org/article.pl?sid=12%2F08%2F17%2F1057207 |title=Solidot的介紹 |accessdate=2020-12-09 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070952/http://internet.solidot.org/article.pl?sid=12%2F08%2F17%2F1057207 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這項工作在2012年7月完成<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/Musopen/status/235757751790366721 |title=Aaron Dunn在Twitter上的留言 |accessdate=2012-08-17 |archive-date=2016-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404050428/https://twitter.com/Musopen/status/235757751790366721 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/Musopen/record-and-release-free-music-without-copyrights/posts/266390 |title=Done! |author=Dunn, Aaron |date=13 July 2012 |publisher=Kickstarter |accessdate=2014-09-20 |archive-date=2020-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301152603/https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/Musopen/record-and-release-free-music-without-copyrights/posts/266390 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，隨後錄製的音樂還被上傳到[[互联网档案馆|互联网档案馆]]。這些音樂的列表在2012年8月完成。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/Musopen/record-and-release-free-music-without-copyrights/posts/288525 |title=Done and Done |author=Dunn, Aaron |date=15 August 2012 |publisher=Kickstarter |accessdate=2014-09-20 |archive-date=2020-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200216101506/https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/Musopen/record-and-release-free-music-without-copyrights/posts/288525 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年9月，Musopen在Kickstarter发起新的募捐活动来录制[[弗雷德里克·肖邦|弗雷德里克·肖邦]]完成的作品。募捐活动取得了成功，所获的资金比目标的75,000美元多出了15,000美元。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/Musopen/set-chopin-free | title=Set Chopin Free | publisher=Aaron Dunn/Kickstarter | accessdate=11 September 2013 | archive-date=2020-11-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111221314/http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/Musopen/set-chopin-free/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 在线音乐库 ==

Musopen网站采用类似于商业内容提供者的经营模式，即一部分内容免费发布，但增值下载要求会员费。活页乐谱可全部免费下载，而且录音可以通过HTML5或[[Flashplayer|Flashplayer]]播放。免费用户可以下载录音，但仅限每天下载20首；会员缴纳年费55美元可不受限制的下载无损音乐；捐助者一年缴纳240美元可要求额外录音（2014年1月价格）。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://musopen.org/page/signup/ |title=Sign Up |author=Musopen Inc. |accessdate=1 Jan 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6MJCf5hIU?url=https://musopen.org/page/signup/ |archivedate=2014-01-01 }} ()</ref>

